<% include partials/header %>

<div class="header1-image">
  <div class="header-container container">
    <h2 class="header-content">Prices and Packages</h2>
    <p class="header-content">Do you need to build a custom application? We can help! Send us your inquiries.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="container">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-12">
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h3>Prices and Quotes</h3>
          <p>Do you have an idea for the next best application, but don't know how to build it? Then you've come to the right place. We are a company solely dedicated to building powerful, functional applications using a serverside framework called node.js.</p>

          <p>Below are estimates of packages based on most requested services. These are not exact prices, however, if you fill out the form with details about your application, our development team will reach out to you within 48 hours with an official quote and timeframe for your application. Let's work together and turn your dream application into a reality! We know you've got some great ideas!</p>

          <p>Lastly, the best part is, once your application is done development, it is completely yours! We do not take any rights or royalties for your application once development is completed.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>


<div class="prices">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row" id="quote">
      <div class="col-md-12 col-sm-12">
        <form action="/quote" method="POST" class="quote">
          <i class="fas fa-quote-right"></i>
          <h2>Get A Quote Today!</h2>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label>Name</label>
            <input type="text" class="form-control" name="quote[name]" placeholder="Name">
          </div>

          <div class="form-group">
            <label>Max Budget</label>
            <input type="text" class="form-control" name="quote[maxBudget]" placeholder="Name">
          </div>

          <div class="form-group">
            <label>Email Address</label>
            <input type="text" class="form-control" name="quote[emailAddress]" placeholder="Name">
          </div>

          <div class="form-group">
            <label>Country</label>
            <input type="text" class="form-control" name="quote[country]" placeholder="Name">
          </div>

          <div class="form-group">
            <label>Industry Type</label>
            <input type="text" class="form-control" name="quote[industry]" placeholder="Name">
          </div>

          <div class="form-group">
            <label>Give us some details on the application you would like!</label>
            <textarea class="form-control" rows="5" placeholder="Provide some more details..."></textarea>
          </div>

          <button class="btn btn-success">Submit</button>
        </form>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</div>


